          <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>美国一般 7-15 个工作日，偏远地区可能多 2-3 天。发货后你会收到追踪号，可以随时查看物流状态。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          <span>💪 质量怎么样？容易坏吗？</span>
          <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>我们使用热熔工艺，豆子之间结合非常牢固。正常使用（挂钥匙、背包）完全没问题。但毕竟是手工品，不要故意摔砸或者泡水哦。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          <span>🎨 可以定制吗？</span>
          <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>当然可以！点击<a href="/pages/custom">这里</a>看定制流程。可以定制图案、文字、颜色搭配，定制款一般需要 3-5 天制作时间。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          <span>🔄 不喜欢能退吗？</span>
          <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>30天无理由退换！如果不喜欢，全额退款。因为运费比产品贵，退货就不用了，直接送给你或者送给朋友吧。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          <span>🎁 包装怎么样？适合送礼吗？</span>
          <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>我们专门设计了品牌包装盒，打开有仪式感。内含感谢卡和像素贴纸，直接送人完全没问题，不用再额外包装。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 悬浮购买栏（移动端显示） -->
  <div class="sticky-buy-bar" id="stickyBar">
    <div class="sticky-info">
      <img src="{{ placeholder_thumbnail_1 }}" class="sticky-img" alt="product">
      <div class="sticky-text">
        <span class="sticky-name">{{ placeholder_product_name }}</span>
        <span class="sticky-price">${{ placeholder_price }}</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <button class="pixel-btn" onclick="addToCart()">立即购买</button>
  </div>

</div>

<!-- JavaScript -->
<script>
// 数量选择
function updateQty(change) {
  const input = document.getElementById('quantity');
  let val = parseInt(input.value) + change;
  if (val >= 1 && val <= 10) {
    input.value = val;
  }
}

// 加入购物车
function addToCart() {
  // TODO: 接入 Shopify 购物车逻辑
  const btn = document.querySelector('.btn-primary');
  btn.innerHTML = '<span class="btn-icon">✅</span><span>ADDED!</span>';
  btn.classList.add('added');
  
  // 播放像素音效（可选）
  playPixelSound();
  
  setTimeout(() => {
    btn.innerHTML = '<span class="btn-icon">🛒</span><span class="btn-text">ADD TO CART</span><span class="btn-price">${{ placeholder_price }}</span>';
    btn.classList.remove('added');
  }, 2000);
}

// 像素音效
function playPixelSound() {
  // TODO: 添加 8-bit 音效
  console.log('🎵 Playing 8-bit sound');
}

// FAQ 展开/收起
function toggleFaq(btn) {
  const item = btn.parentElement;
  const answer = item.querySelector('.faq-answer');
  const icon = btn.querySelector('.faq-icon');
  
  item.classList.toggle('open');
  icon.textContent = item.classList.contains('open') ? '−' : '+';
}

// 动态库存/浏览人数（模拟）
function updateUrgencyStats() {
  const stockEl = document.getElementById('stockCount');
  const viewerEl = document.getElementById('viewerCount');
  
  if (stockEl) {
    let stock = parseInt(stockEl.textContent);
    if (Math.random() > 0.7 && stock > 5) {
      stockEl.textContent = stock - 1;
    }
  }
  
  if (viewerEl) {
    let viewers = parseInt(viewerEl.textContent);
    viewers += Math.floor(Math.random() * 3) - 1;
    viewerEl.textContent = Math.max(50, viewers);
  }
}

setInterval(updateUrgencyStats, 5000);

// 悬浮栏显示/隐藏
let lastScroll = 0;
window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
  const stickyBar = document.getElementById('stickyBar');
  const currentScroll = window.pageYOffset;
  
  if (currentScroll > 800) {
    stickyBar.classList.add('show');
  } else {
    stickyBar.classList.remove('show');
  }
  
  lastScroll = currentScroll;
});

// 图片切换
document.querySelectorAll('.pd-thumb').forEach(thumb => {
  thumb.addEventListener('click', function() {
    document.querySelectorAll('.pd-thumb').forEach(t => t.classList.remove('active'));
    this.classList.add('active');
    // TODO: 切换主图
  });
});

// 变体选择
document.querySelectorAll('.variant-btn').forEach(btn => {
  btn.addEventListener('click', function() {
    document.querySelectorAll('.variant-btn').forEach(b => b.classList.remove('selected'));
    this.classList.add('selected');
  });
});

// 像素粒子效果
document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
  const particlesContainer = document.getElementById('pixelParticles');
  if (particlesContainer) {
    for (let i = 0; i < 20; i++) {
      const particle = document.createElement('div');
      particle.className = 'pixel-particle';
      particle.style.left = Math.random() * 100 + '%';
      particle.style.animationDelay = Math.random() * 2 + 's';
      particle.style.backgroundColor = ['#FF6B6B', '#4ECDC4', '#FFE66D', '#95E1D3'][Math.floor(Math.random() * 4)];
      particlesContainer.appendChild(particle);
    }
  }
});
</script>

